content: Great to have you onboard as CTO! Some additional context. All services and script file are ready, the only issue is that some of them other than memory_service might still have mock directives in them that need to be removed for full deployment. We are not going to strip functionality as it has all been tested and would be very time consuming and resource intensive for you to rebuild everything. Other than that, it sounds like you're up to speed, what's next?
